<Body>
	<Title>深圳龙岗区一家工厂数百人食物中毒</Title>
	<ReportTime type="absTime">2008年1月10日</ReportTime>
	<Content>
		<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e1"><Time tid="t1" type="relTime">昨天下午三四时</Time>，位于<Location lid="l1">深圳龙岗区平湖街道一家港资厂</Location>发生一起罕见的<Participant sid="s1">员工</Participant>集体<Denoter did="d1" type="emergency">食物中毒</Denoter>事件</Event>，<Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e2"><Participant sid="s2">知情人士</Participant><Denoter did="d2" type="statement">透露</Denoter><Object oid="o2">中毒人数</Object>约700人</Event>，但<Event eid="e3"><Participant sid="s3">平湖街道办</Participant><Denoter did="d3" type="operation">统计</Denoter>的<Object oid="o3">中毒人数</Object>为308人</Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e4"><Time tid="t4" type="relTime">目前</Time>，<Participant sid="s4">大部分员工</Participant>经已<Denoter did="d4" type="stateChange">治愈</Denoter></Event><Event eid="e5"><Denoter did="d5" type="movement">回厂</Denoter></Event>，至<Event eid="e6"><Participant sid="s6">记者</Participant><Denoter did="d6" type="operation">截稿</Denoter></Event>止，<Event eid="e7">仍有<Participant oid="o7" type="recipient">部分员工</Participant>在<Location lid="l7">医院</Location>继续<Denoter did="d7" type="operation">治疗</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>

　  <Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e8"><Participant sid="s8">事发的工厂</Participant><Denoter did="d8" type="statement">是</Denoter>一家名为“港华鸿记厂”的<Object oid="o8">港资厂</Object></Event>，该<Event eid="e9">工厂<Denoter did="d9" type="statement">有</Denoter><Participant oid="o9">员工</Participant>近三千人</Event>，<Event eid="e10">主要<Denoter did="d10" type="statement">生产</Denoter><Object oid="o10">相框</Object></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e11"><Time tid="t11" type="relTime">昨天下午三四时许</Time>，该厂<Participant sid="s11">数百工人</Participant>陆续<Denoter did="d11" type="stateChange">出现</Denoter>头晕、头痛、呕吐、腹痛、四肢麻木、心慌等<Object oid="o11">症状</Object></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence>由于出现此症状的工人越来越多，<Event eid="e12">该工厂的<Participant sid="s12">负责人</Participant>马上<Denoter did="d12" type="operation">组织</Denoter><Object oid="o12">车辆</Object></Event><Event eid="e13">将出现症状的<Participant sid="s13">员工</Participant>分别<Denoter did="d13" type="movement">送往</Denoter><Location lid="l13">平湖人民医院、山厦医院、深联医院、横岗人民医院、沙湾医院急诊科</Location>等几家医院</Event><Event eid="e14">紧急<Denoter did="d14" type="operation">施救</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
           </Content>
